Strategy: ( Or, How to lose most gracefully )

 Too much of anything will lose the game for you!
 Make your moves quickly, do thinking while screens are loading. The clock is
              ticking ALL the time!
 Best approach seems to be a careful balance of all game elements:
  Intelligence gathering - Infiltration.
  Organizing resistance.
  Search and find.
 Knock out targets early. More than three or four waste time.
 More than two trips to War Room is risky.
  Don't stay for more than 12 months, or you'll be arrested.
 Follow leads till all used, (better than losing two months a pop at an empty
              country)
 Keep track of where you've been, second visits are costly.
 Dare I say it... Luck and hunches often make or break the game!

